edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.configuration
Class Frame

java.lang.Object
  edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.configuration.Frame

public class Frame
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a configuration frame within a Xilinx FPGA. This object has a frame address, frame data, and a configuration tag indicating whether the frame has been configured or not.
